ish Kieran, Declan, Brendan, Dermot, Donal, Fidelma, Fintan, Liam, Mairead, Sean Patrick.","Irish: shortened Anglicized form of Gaelic <b>Ó hAonghusa</b> ‘descendant of <i>Aonghus</i>’; see   Angus  , and compare   McGinnis  ."]},{"name":"Anguish","meanings":["Scottish and English: from an English mishearing of the Scottish Gaelic personal name <i>Aonghus</i>, see   Angus   and   McAninch  ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Fimmghuala De Angus was born about 1035, in Douglas and Angus, Forfarshire, Scotland, her father, Sinill Douglas Cameron 1st Chief of Clan Cameron, Mormaer, Dubacan of Angus, was 24 and her mother, Marion MacKenneth, was 32. She had at least 2 sons and 1 daughter with Lulach of Scotland “The Fool” MacRory 1st King of Scotland, Prince of Moray."},"et":{"about 1035–":"umbes 1035–Surnud","1030–1099":"1030–1099","1035–Female":"1035–Surnud","1045–Female":"1045–Surnud","1033–1058":"1033–1058","1020–Male":"1020–Surnud","1050–Female":"1050–Surnud","1050–1085":"1050–1085","1058–1097":"1058–1097","–1085":"–1085","1012–1050":"1012–1050","1005–Female":"1005–Surnud","Abt. 1050":"umbes 1050","about 1050":"umbes 1050","1033":"1033","1099":"1099","1097":"1097","1020":"1020","1085":"1085","1030":"1030","1050":"1050","1005":"1005","1058":"1058","1035":"1035","1012":"1012","1045":"1045","about 1035":"umbes 1035","before 1030":"1030","Douglas and Angus, Forfarshire, Scotland":"Douglas and Angus, Forfarshire, Scotland","Scotland":"Scotland","Morayshire, Scotland":"Elginshire, Scotland"},"fi":{"about 1035–":"noin 1035–Kuollut","1030–1099":"1030–1099","1035–Female":"1035–Kuollut","1045–Female":"1045–Kuollut","1033–1058":"1033–1058","1020–Male":"1020–Kuollut","1050–Female":"1050–Kuollut","1050–1085":"1050–1085","1058–1097":"1058–1097","–1085":"–1085","1012–1050":"1012–1050","1005–Female":"1005–Kuollut","Abt. 1050":"noin 1050","about 1050":"noin 1050","1033":"1033","1099":"1099","1097":"1097","1020":"1020","1085":"1085","1030":"1030","1050":"1050","1005":"1005","1058":"1058","1